Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為所有人都怕你們就錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是傑哈特·葛雷德同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會保護你和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來！ 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是傑哈特 發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達從視野裏消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是移民計劃失敗的受害者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在火星圈的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新興國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在嚴酷環境下生活的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回那座名為「地球」的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策劃起了規模宏大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘襲擊事件的後續報道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方發言人宣稱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次襲擊事件中無人傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 關於維甘機動戰士的入侵途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據稱還在調查中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都在說這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 維甘攻來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算他們再來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台白色機動戰士也會把他們打回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒趕上昨天那場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場面可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 從沒見過那種白色機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是軍隊的新機型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 千萬記住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你駕駛高達的事要絕對保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘的目標恐怕是高達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白其中的含義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有小道消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 老爸隻字未提
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想加入我們社團了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來為昨天的事道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 關於那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 要保密是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們倆的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待比賽那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 什麼時候勾搭上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 青春就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情和戀情和機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差戀情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正明白就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的青春從此開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聯邦軍進行了情報管制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是通過戰鬥發生的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和現場殘留的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經圈定了高達的所在區域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以鍛造機動戰士聞名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野家族的私人宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆的父親是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦軍總部BIGRING司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原高達駕駛者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達被藏匿在亞瑟姆家的可能性極高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只換軸承果然作用不大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 我也想加入機動戰士社團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次自己說沒興趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威 有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定可以幫上你們的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 太厲害了 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程序稍作調整就變化這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 允許你加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離大會不遠了 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別硬掰 夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄壞的話就前功盡棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…擔心 就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點 夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說加點機油吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的零件全在這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎略顯疲態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查的進展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 除一個地方以外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經搜遍了整個地區
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果和之前相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達就藏在明日野家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點確信無疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那裏警衛森嚴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裏不是為做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為實現維甘的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你父親是BIGRING的司令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裏有很多機動戰士的相關資料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有 但那是爸爸的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能隨便給別人看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能找到提高性能用的珍貴資料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了變得更強 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想在比賽裏獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老爸見識下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後再向父親道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了讓我們的機體變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過別亂翻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去下父親的書房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亂碰裏面的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群有意思的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個長髮的人好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是BIGRING司令的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士相關的書是這本…這本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 我去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著走廊 到底右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幢房子不像能藏得下機動戰士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 剩下的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士模擬格鬥大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托爾迪亞的年輕技師們齊聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝配機動戰士和負責操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的智慧 熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將在此碰撞出熾熱的火花！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的願望只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥 獲勝 奪冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是48支隊伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠如願以償的只有一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是那支隊伍最後勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得榮耀的桂冠呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一場就是決賽了 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就一直沒看見他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 計劃按時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會馬上前往匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一支進入決賽的隊伍出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈特曼校隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛者是法比·德魯斯緹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拍對手隊伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給亞瑟姆鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯大人 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離決賽開始不到5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特幹什麼去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘的機動戰士又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你去哪 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決賽馬上開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這裏拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回來 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然在迎戰 但堅持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們攔不住敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的麻煩 但無礙大局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 趁我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火 開火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分了 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯大人 情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 再等會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 設定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗這招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裏去了 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 拖延太久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果大會改期了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 據說維甘又來進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是被那台白色機動戰士打回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 亞瑟姆和傑哈特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他們請假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是菲利特麾下的聯邦軍設施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把高達藏在這裏可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 菲利特會保護我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論遇到什麼敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達被運出明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達烏內斯總部下令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續潛伏直至成功奪取高達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我剛才鬆了一口氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業儀式 與好友的告別
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為戰士的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悲劇的開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業儀式上的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR是XRounder專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zedas的改進型機體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的駕駛者會讓機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發揮出不同的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.07,0:24:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder專用機更是如此

